    {
      "area": "Event store immutability",
      "reason": "By design and by regulatory requirement, events cannot be modified or deleted. This is intentional rigidity — it IS the feature. However, it means mistakes in events require compensating events rather than corrections, and GDPR right-to-erasure requires crypto-shredding or similar techniques rather than deletion."
