      "area": "Aggregate boundary (one aggregate per loan application)",
      "reason": "The loan application aggregate must remain the transactional boundary. Splitting it later (e.g., separating borrower info from loan terms) would require event stream migration, which is operationally expensive."
    },
    {
      "area": "Event serialization format",
      "reason": "The chosen serialization format (JSON, Avro, Protobuf) for events becomes a long-term commitment since events are stored forever. Switching formats later requires either dual-format support or full migration."
    }
  ],

